{"tid":2080632,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"（泡菜）苦等多月 我大blackpink 終於回歸！","createTime":"2020-06-26T14:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T08:11:22.000Z","uid":104308,"like":9,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f3ec6958c25ab205a8653dae65b7ba6ed6274f71","tid":2080632,"uid":104308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T14:31:10.000Z","msg":"大家睇左mv未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ioNng23DkIM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FioNng23DkIM&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h6d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=c8e8a0c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ioNng23DkIM</a><br />\n<br />\n睇返我之前啲po 就知我blackpink鐵粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慘在等到我人都老 得嗰幾隻歌！<br />\n先容許我訴下苦<br />\n今次首歌係幾好 但得嗰三分鐘 聽聽下冇左...下 播完啦？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n造型我冇乜挑剔 完顏團 但係jennie個頭係發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMv rose掂比例極少 好心yg唔好偏心到出面得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以上都係對yg既不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌係真係幾正 希望bp 回歸大發 九月正規專輯可以有更多好歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後送上幾張jisoo美照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aovCwZA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaovCwZA.png&h=82711172&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/99pWNx0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2